skyproc

Class SPDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • skyproc.SPDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Mod>

    public class SPDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Mod>
    An organized set of Mods forces load order. It is somewhat unnecessary at the moment, but it will offer more powerful and unique functionality later on as SkyProc develops.

      • queryMajor

                 GRUP_TYPE... grup_types)

        Parameters:

        grup_types - GRUPs to look in.
        Returns:
        True if FormID exists in the database.

      • getMajor

        public static MajorRecord getMajor(FormID query)
        Querys the Global Database and returns the first record that matches the FormID. It limits its search to the given GRUP types for speed reasons.
        Parameters:
        query - FormID to look for.
        Returns:
        The first MajorRecord that matches, or MajorRecord.NULL if none were found.

      • getMajor
